Monthly initiations

Definition

Tab & Variable Definition
Table The Table tab shows the number and percentage of patients included in your cohort by calendar month. Each patient is represented once in this table.
Month Calendar month and patients with missing inclusion dates.
Previous 12 months This column represents all patients included in the cohort in the 365 days before the end of user-defined reporting period. The month containing the end of reporting date will therefore be split between two years of inclusion.

For example, if the end of reporting date is chosen as 15 January 2020, in the table January will represent the number of patients included from 16 January 2019 to 31 January 2019 plus from 1 January 2020 to 15 January 2020.
Full programme This describes all patients entering the cohort prior to the user-defined end of reporting date.
Monthly initiations The Monthly initiations tab graphically describes the information within the Previous 12 months column of the Table tab. The month containing the end of reporting date is coloured red for emphasis. The start of reporting date is not used to generate this graph.
Quarterly initiations The Quarterly initiations tab depicts cohort inclusions by quarter to provide a longer historical overview. No inclusions on, or after the end of reporting date are represented. The start of reporting date is not used to generate this graph.

Definitions

Tab & Variable Definition
Both tabs These tabs provides aggregated figures for patients at the time of programme entry.
Reporting period User provided dates define the reporting period used for this column. Patients are included if they initiated treatment on or after the report start date and before the report end date.
Previous 12 months This column represents all patients included in the cohort in the 365 days before the end of user-defined reporting period.
Full programme This describes all patients entering the cohort prior to the user-defined end of reporting date.
Age, gender, BMI, CD4 count & WHO Stage All characteristics are described from treatment initiation. Where this is not available, the most recent value prior to treatment initiation is recorded. Data recorded after treatment initation will not be reflected in this table.
